---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Music'>
	<article>
		<div class='textWrapper'>
			<p>
				<span class='highlight'>Henrii Havaas</span> was born in <span class='highlight'>Oslo</span
				>, Norway, and discovered the joy of photography as a young girl.

				<p>
					Everything she knows about <span class='highlight'>photography</span> is self-taught. She has
					a special eye for capturing a truthful essence of nature and people in her photos. Natural
					light is her favorite style to use and to create images, that exude purity, liveliness, and
					simplicity.
				</p>

				<p>
					She focuses on <span class='highlight'>Fine Art Photography</span> and is driven by storytelling
					and authenticity.
				</p>

				<p>
					In addition to being a photographer, she is also a <span class='highlight'
						>music designer</span
					>, <span class='highlight'>embodiment teacher</span> and
					<span class='highlight'>facilitator of art and culture events</span>.
				</p>

				<p>
					Henrii is currently based in Oslo and part of the Selah Sleep team, a wake-up light and
					sound project.
				</p>
			</p>
		</div>

